<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[المواردة]</span>: وارَدَه: أي ورده معه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[ي]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[المواراة]</span>: واراه: أي ستره.<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> يُواارِي سَوْآتِكُمْ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
